skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: random noun
des:
Ask Alexa for a random noun, by saying "Alexa, tell Random Noun give me a random noun!". The skill will then return a random noun from a list of hundreds of common nouns!

You can use these random nouns as inspiration for jokes or stories!
